    "note": "Stage-8 (Fable) adjudication — full sweep of all 132 rows, 2 structures (be (not) allowed to + base; let + person + base, no \"to\"). Answers lens verified BOTH CLEAN: be-allowed-to has correct be-agreement + base verb after \"allowed to\" (no -ing/past); let has NO \"to\" after let+person + correct don't/doesn't negatives; all distractors (missing-be, let+to, lets-not, -ing) genuinely wrong. Translation CLEAN (dürfen→be allowed to, lassen→let; \"it depends\"→\"Es kommt darauf an\"). Fixed: register 1 (\"be-Form\" in mc.005 prompt → \"Form von be\"); level-gloss added pedagogical glosses for granted A2 words (face/hours/corridor/dictionary/test/charge/tours). ~115 audited grants (permission base verbs + theme nouns + decoys). Reworded 8 long phrasal-verb def-leaks off their headword tokens (to-dye-your-hair etc.); dropped 2 too-short anagrams (is/to); relabeled group-sorts to ✓/✗; fixed sb chip budgets + an it-depends lang-evidence quirk. 0 fix, 0 drop → approve."
